.claude/settings.local.json

# Agent rules: the canonical, git-tracked home is `.agents/rules/*.mdc`. The
# `.cursor/rules` and `.claude/rules` trees are symlink mirrors regenerated by
# `pnpm rules:sync` (wired into `prepare`); ignore them so only canonical is tracked.
.cursor/rules
.claude/rules
